    <section class="prose">
        <p>a single-player text horror game that runs in your terminal.</p>
        <p>
            you wake at the bottom of an abandoned mineshaft. the surface
            above is dying. the lip of the shaft curls inward. there is no
            climbing back. the only way is down.
        </p>
        <p>
            every player carves into the walls. you will read what others
            left at the depths you reach. they will read what you leave.
            the wall remembers everyone.
        </p>
        <p>the queen waits at depth two hundred.</p>
